==English==

===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

#To deny the truth of (a statement or statements).
#:''His testimony '''contradicts''' hers.''
#To make a statement denying the truth of the statement(s) made by (a person).
#:''Everything he says '''contradicts''' me.''

